# 🌾 AgriGuard — Agro-Advisory Agent for Nepali Smallholder Farmers

**AgriGuard** is a multi-agent advisory system that gives smallholder farmers in
Nepal fast, localized answers on crop timing, market prices, and pest/disease
management — with hard, deterministic safety guardrails around chemical and
pesticide advice, so the agent can never become the source of a harmful dosage
recommendation.

Built for the Kaggle **"5-Day AI Agents: Intensive Vibe Coding Course"** capstone
(*Kaggriculture*), submitted to the **Agents for Good** track.

![AgriGuard interface](agriguard-ui.png)

